                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <span style="float:right;">
                        <a style="text-decoration: none;" href="/Service">Services</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;
                        <a style="text-decoration: none;" href="mailto:binkod.info@gmail.com">Write to us</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
